POLOKWANE – Mayor John Mpe delivered his State of the City Address today (June 24). The event was held at the Jack Botes Hall and members of various opposition parties were in attendance. After the mayor’s address, Review spoke to EFF Councillor Dinah Mohlabeng and FF Plus Councillor Susan Maritz Clarke to hear what they had to say about the address. Also read: Political parties have mixed feelings ahead of the State of the City Address 